Meet <b>Nick9494</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Nick9494 has lived at <a href='/home/?user=transam'>5130 Timberwolf Way</a> in the trendy neighborhood of Metro Park since August 15, 2004.  He's enjoyed his first year in Millsberry a whole lot, and he's looking forward to staying for many years to come!<br><br>Though it's still early in the school year at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a>, Nick9494 has already proven himself to be a star student.  Though he has a wide range of knowledge, Nick9494 does especially well when it comes to math.  On most days, Nick9494 stays after school in the afternoons, doing homework with his friends in the library, lending a hand at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=10">Student Store</a>, or helping younger students with their studies.  Nick9494's caring nature makes him a great tutor!  At the moment, Nick9494 is working on putting together a school trivia team.  Because he's so friendly, Nick9494 is sure to find plenty of volunteers.  <br><br>This hard-working scholar doesn't spend all his time hitting the books, though.  He also loves football!  On weekends during football season, Nick9494 puts on his silver and orange jersey and lucky green cleats, before heading out to play football in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park/">Peabody Park</a>.  Whether he's connecting with a receiver on a perfect pass or making his own run for the end zone, Nick9494 enjoys every aspect of the game.  When he's not busy making plays on the football field, Nick9494 likes to hang out at his best friend's house, tossing around a football in the backyard.<br><br>Nick9494 has recently added a new hobby to his ever-growing list of interests.  He's been into computers for a long time now, but Nick9494 recently decided to try to use his computer for making music.  By taking features from his favorite musical styles (rap, pop, and heavy metal) and mixing them on his computer, Nick9494 has created an entirely new sound!  Once he felt that he had perfected his sound, Nick9494 went down to the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Millsberry Recording Studio</a> and recorded his songs in a real professional setting.  At the end of the session, everyone who had overheard Nick9494's music was really impressed.  Word of his cool, new musical style soon spread throughout Millsberry, and since then, one of Nick9494's tracks has made it all the way to the top of the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top Ten chart.<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Nick9494, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
